1
00:01:10,280 --> 00:01:11,480
Do you think you can catch me?

2
00:01:12,320 --> 00:01:13,160
Let me tell you,

3
00:01:14,160 --> 00:01:15,160
you can't catch me.

4
00:01:23,040 --> 00:01:23,400
You Tong,

5
00:01:24,640 --> 00:01:25,360
tell me everything

6
00:01:26,240 --> 00:01:26,920
you know.

7
00:01:27,720 --> 00:01:28,920
I've already told you.

8
00:01:29,240 --> 00:01:30,760
Everything that happened to your family

9
00:01:31,240 --> 00:01:33,240
is a punishment from heaven.

10
00:01:34,240 --> 00:01:35,520
But you didn't believe it.

11
00:01:41,600 --> 00:01:42,240
You Tong,

12
00:01:43,440 --> 00:01:44,840
stop playing dumb with me.

13
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:47,600
I have plenty of ways to make you talk.

14
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:51,800
Ways?

15
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:56,000
What ways could you possibly have?

16
00:01:57,240 --> 00:01:58,640
I'm not even afraid of death.

17
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:00,320
Do you think I'd fear your threats?

18
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:03,360
You Tong,

19
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:05,920
I know you were used by someone too.

20
00:02:08,800 --> 00:02:09,720
Just tell me

21
00:02:10,360 --> 00:02:10,800
who

22
00:02:11,440 --> 00:02:12,080
he is.

23
00:02:13,280 --> 00:02:14,000
I can help you.

24
00:02:14,880 --> 00:02:15,600
Help me?

25
00:02:16,720 --> 00:02:17,600
It's not that easy.

26
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:21,880
Besides, I don't need your help.

27
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:26,160
From the moment I stepped into this trap,

28
00:02:28,440 --> 00:02:30,160
I was destined to have no way back.

29
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:31,280
No.

30
00:02:32,280 --> 00:02:33,080
With me here,

31
00:02:33,880 --> 00:02:34,800
I can help you.

32
00:02:37,080 --> 00:02:38,520
Just tell me who he is,

33
00:02:39,440 --> 00:02:40,280
and leave the rest to me.

34
00:02:41,600 --> 00:02:42,080
Fine.

35
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:44,160
You said it yourself.

36
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:47,000
I can tell you.

37
00:02:52,280 --> 00:02:54,000
The "he" I just mentioned

38
00:02:55,080 --> 00:02:56,520
is from the Guigu School,

39
00:02:56,520 --> 00:02:57,720
Master Yihe.

40
00:02:58,880 --> 00:02:59,800
And Yihe

41
00:03:00,440 --> 00:03:02,160
is exactly the one you've been searching for,

42
00:03:03,440 --> 00:03:05,000
Liu Jiaquan.

43
00:03:06,880 --> 00:03:07,720
How do you know

44
00:03:08,360 --> 00:03:09,360
I've been looking for him?

45
00:03:10,440 --> 00:03:11,720
I just told you.

46
00:03:12,400 --> 00:03:13,280
Your every move

47
00:03:13,480 --> 00:03:14,480
is under his control.

48
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:16,000
Your family's fate

49
00:03:16,200 --> 00:03:17,160
from the very beginning

50
00:03:17,160 --> 00:03:18,440
was nothing but his conspiracy.

51
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:24,440
Tell me,

52
00:03:26,160 --> 00:03:26,880
where is he?

53
00:03:41,600 --> 00:03:42,120
Chuncheng,

54
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,400
I have something to do, I'm going out.

55
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:55,480
You're finally here.

56
00:03:56,600 --> 00:03:57,600
You knew I was coming.

57
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:00,960
It was you

58
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:03,160
who deliberately let You Tong

59
00:04:03,160 --> 00:04:04,200
tell me your address

60
00:04:04,560 --> 00:04:05,320
to lure me here.

61
00:04:07,880 --> 00:04:08,960
You are much smarter

62
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:11,440
than your father.

63
00:04:13,120 --> 00:04:13,760
So,

64
00:04:15,040 --> 00:04:15,760
my mother,

65
00:04:16,320 --> 00:04:16,880
father,

66
00:04:17,320 --> 00:04:18,040
cousin,

67
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:19,840
and Ba Gu were all killed by you.

68
00:04:19,960 --> 00:04:20,600
That's right.

69
00:04:22,200 --> 00:04:23,600
Even death is too good for them.

70
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:30,280
This is all your family's

71
00:04:31,560 --> 00:04:32,880
deserved fate.

72
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:40,720
Come back to the police station with me

73
00:04:41,720 --> 00:04:42,960
and give everyone an explanation.

74
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:43,840
An explanation?

75
00:04:46,880 --> 00:04:47,840
That depends on whether

76
00:04:47,840 --> 00:04:49,320
you have what it takes.

77
00:04:59,760 --> 00:05:01,200
Today I will send you on your way,

78
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:02,880
so you can go see your

79
00:05:02,880 --> 00:05:04,000
treacherous father.

80
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:05,320
Even if I die,

81
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:07,440
I won't let you off.

82
00:05:39,760 --> 00:05:40,400
Inspector!

83
00:05:41,080 --> 00:05:41,600
Master!

84
00:05:49,440 --> 00:05:50,000
Qingqing,

85
00:05:52,440 --> 00:05:53,600
why did you come here?

86
00:05:54,320 --> 00:05:55,160
Why?

87
00:05:56,200 --> 00:05:57,280
Master...

88
00:05:58,160 --> 00:05:59,720
how many times have I told you

89
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:02,720
not to interfere in the Huang family's affairs?

90
00:06:03,520 --> 00:06:04,640
Why didn't you listen?

91
00:06:04,840 --> 00:06:06,200
Why didn't you listen?

92
00:06:07,080 --> 00:06:07,840
Master,

93
00:06:09,080 --> 00:06:10,960
why did you do this?

94
00:06:11,520 --> 00:06:12,960
Everything I did

95
00:06:14,880 --> 00:06:16,840
was forced upon me by Huang Zhenyue.

96
00:06:19,320 --> 00:06:20,880
This is the Huang family's

97
00:06:21,880 --> 00:06:23,320
deserved fate.

98
00:06:27,960 --> 00:06:28,840
Why?

99
00:06:31,760 --> 00:06:33,080
Why?

100
00:06:49,840 --> 00:06:50,960
The person in this photo...

101
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:52,520
Is it you?

102
00:06:53,520 --> 00:06:54,000
Liu...

103
00:06:54,840 --> 00:06:55,200
Jia...

104
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:56,520
quan.

105
00:07:01,600 --> 00:07:02,440
Liu Jiaquan.

106
00:07:05,200 --> 00:07:06,200
It's been a long time since I heard

107
00:07:06,200 --> 00:07:07,640
anyone call me by that name.

108
00:07:16,400 --> 00:07:16,880
I know

109
00:07:17,840 --> 00:07:18,640
you resent my father.

110
00:07:19,400 --> 00:07:20,080
But why did you

111
00:07:20,840 --> 00:07:22,200
use such cruel methods

112
00:07:22,200 --> 00:07:23,160
to murder my mother,

113
00:07:23,840 --> 00:07:25,200
and my cousin,

114
00:07:26,080 --> 00:07:27,000
and Ba Gu?

115
00:07:29,440 --> 00:07:30,320
Since you want to hear it so much,

116
00:07:32,960 --> 00:07:34,080
I'll tell you about it.

117
00:07:36,760 --> 00:07:38,080
This all started

118
00:07:39,160 --> 00:07:40,720
after I was captured.

119
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:45,760
Back then,

120
00:07:47,280 --> 00:07:48,320
I was captured by the enemy.

121
00:07:58,320 --> 00:08:00,320
To protect my good brother,

122
00:08:00,760 --> 00:08:01,640
Huang Zhenyue,

123
00:08:02,080 --> 00:08:03,200
and keep the military secrets,

124
00:08:04,840 --> 00:08:05,760
I suffered

125
00:08:06,960 --> 00:08:09,320
unbearable military torture.

126
00:08:19,520 --> 00:08:20,720
Those days

127
00:08:22,320 --> 00:08:23,400
were completely dark.

128
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:25,640
Every minute,

129
00:08:26,320 --> 00:08:27,320
every second,

130
00:08:27,960 --> 00:08:30,000
was pure agony for me.

131
00:08:30,320 --> 00:08:31,400
Even so,

132
00:08:32,400 --> 00:08:33,840
I didn't reveal

133
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:35,320
a single piece of military intelligence.

134
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:37,280
Later, the enemy wasn't satisfied,

135
00:08:39,160 --> 00:08:40,840
so they threatened me with my family

136
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:43,280
to make me spill the intelligence.

137
00:08:57,960 --> 00:08:58,840
I was

138
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:01,400
on the verge of a breakdown.

139
00:09:02,520 --> 00:09:03,320
I was going crazy.

140
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:04,640
Later, I found out from

141
00:09:04,640 --> 00:09:05,960
the enemy's mouth that

142
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:08,200
when they found my

143
00:09:08,200 --> 00:09:09,080
family,

144
00:09:10,720 --> 00:09:12,320
my family was already dead.

145
00:09:13,320 --> 00:09:14,840
They died a violent death.

146
00:09:18,080 --> 00:09:19,200
The enemy was unwilling to accept

147
00:09:20,840 --> 00:09:22,720
that the leverage they could have used to threaten me

148
00:09:24,400 --> 00:09:25,840
was gone just like that.

149
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:27,760
Father!

150
00:09:28,640 --> 00:09:29,200
Mother!

151
00:09:30,400 --> 00:09:31,600
My dear wife!

152
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:34,280
You bunch of jerks!

153
00:09:34,600 --> 00:09:35,240
Jerks!

154
00:09:35,240 --> 00:09:36,320
They took my parents' corpses...

155
00:09:36,320 --> 00:09:38,080
Let me go!

156
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:39,960
And my wife,

157
00:09:39,960 --> 00:09:41,600
even my unborn child...

158
00:09:41,960 --> 00:09:42,480
Father!

159
00:09:43,040 --> 00:09:43,840
They were...

160
00:09:44,440 --> 00:09:45,320
Kicked once,

161
00:09:46,320 --> 00:09:47,080
twice,

162
00:09:48,720 --> 00:09:49,800
three times...
